{"tid":1513560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵人入嚟吹水","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:30:03.000Z","uid":171783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"edbb4d116403c1bbb0c756f53b208d88ead62cdd","tid":1513560,"uid":171783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:25:06.000Z","msg":"吹水谷招人<br />\n招收中意打機同熱愛動漫嘅你加入<br />\n唔開心嘅都可以入嚟傾訴<br />\n因為我自己都放緊負想搵人傾訴<br />\n入到嚟吹咩都得<br />\n記住唔好喺谷入面隨便公開講自己個人嘅嘢<br />\n冇咩特別規制<br />\n不定時開discord吹水打機<br />\n歡迎你嘅加入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7870e6b4723c617a2c5731e266b6466c6ae95e7e","tid":1513560,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"b54a12260cec618a